Supports Straight Color Assignments And Aliases (frontend for the complexity of terminal handling):

{{{
$ echo "Text" | colorize --background green --foreground yellow
}}}
<p align = "center">
https://codemiscs.googlecode.com/git/shots/Colorize/ColorizeTextCustom.png
</p>

{{{
$ cat ./README | colorize --background blue --foreground green
}}}
<p align = "center">
https://codemiscs.googlecode.com/git/shots/Colorize/ColorizeFileCustom.png
</p>

Prettifies Message Logging levels:

{{{
$ echo "This is an error" | colorize --error
}}}
<p align = "center">
https://codemiscs.googlecode.com/git/shots/Colorize/ColorizeError.png
</p>

{{{
$ echo "This is a warning" | colorize --warning
}}}
<p align = "center">
https://codemiscs.googlecode.com/git/shots/Colorize/ColorizeWarning.png
</p>

{{{
$ echo "This is a message" | colorize --info
}}}
<p align = "center">
https://codemiscs.googlecode.com/git/shots/Colorize/ColorizeInfo.png
