Highlights Lines & Patterns:
{{{
$ echo -e "When done." | colorize --match done --info
}}}

{{{
$ echo -e "When\nerror" | colorize --line error --error
}}}

Increases Readability:

{{{
$ cat file | colorize smart | less
}}}
